These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: british, brazilian, nigerian, mexican
1. the brazilian is in an odd position##4
2. the mexican is between the british and the brazilian##2
3. the mexican is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | british | mexican | brazilian | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, pomegranate, peach, onion
1. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating onion##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | pomegranate | pepper | onion | peach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, romance, western, fantasy
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
2. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching western movies is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching romance movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | action | fantasy | western | romance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, golf, tennis, badminton
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
2. the person who's sport is tennis is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's sport is tennis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | golf | cricket | badminton | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, parkour, soccer, tennis
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | tennis | volleyball | soccer | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, italian, dutch, argentine
1. the italian is on the far right##1
2. the italian is on the left or right of the argentine##3
3. the dutch is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | dutch | australian | argentine | italian |

