.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, gospel, techno, trance
1. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
2. the fan of country is between the fan of gospel and the fan of techno##2
3. the fan of country is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |  3  |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | trance | gospel | country | techno |

