1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is writing##2
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Hobby   | chess | writing | puzzles | rock-climbing |

