.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, train, airplane, bike
1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the train is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | airplane | train | bike | taxi |

