.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, soccer, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Sport   | soccer | skateboarding | lacrosse | parkour |

